title: Paris Fashion Week: Day 8
text: Paris Fashion Week: Day 8 Chanel stole the show on the last day of Paris Fashion week with a bold event that featured an actual rocket launch. Here Gigi Hadid walks the runway in a houndstooth jumpsuit. Dark colors and patterns dominated the Chanel show. Dark colors and patterns dominated the Chanel show.  //usat.ly/2mBrMX9   Paris Fashion Week: Day 8 None Chanel stole the show on the last day of Paris Fashion week with a bold event that featured an actual rocket launch. Here Gigi Hadid walks the runway in a houndstooth jumpsuit. Dark colors and patterns dominated the Chanel show. Pascal Le Segretain, Getty Images None Gigi's sister Bella Hadid was also in the show, wearing a navy dress with black and white detailing. Pascal Le Segretain, Getty Images None Kendall Jenner also joined the group of famous models at the show, wearing a classic skirt suit with a bold pattern and fur cuffs. IAN LANGSDON, EPA A model walks in one of the few pants looks from the collection. Pascal Le Segretain, Getty Images None Big and bold silhouettes were also prominent in the looks. IAN LANGSDON, EPA The intergalactic theme gave the show a dark color palette, with lots of grays. Pascal Le Segretain, Getty Images None Another model walks in an oversized coat in the Chanel show. IAN LANGSDON, EPA The Chanel show also included a lot of chokers and headbands as accessories. IAN LANGSDON, EPA Chanel even had a spot for pint-sized model Hudson Kroenig. Pascal Le Segretain, Getty Images None Celebrities flocked to the Chanel show, including former model Cara Delevingne, who's been spotted elsewhere at Paris Fashion Week. Pascal Le Segretain, Getty Images None Pharrell Williams also attended the show.
